{"product_id":"aseel-attar-roll-on-6ml-al-saalim-perfumers-alcohol-free","title":"Aseel Attar (Roll On 6ml) | Al-Saalim Perfumers | Alcohol Free","description":"\u003cp\u003eExperience the deep, bold and traditional fragrance of Aseel Attar by Al-Saalim Perfumers.\u003c\/p\u003e\n\u003cp\u003eYe attar apni strong, warm aur classic aroma ke liye jaana jaata hai, jo ek royal aur confident feel deta hai.\u003c\/p\u003e\n\u003cp\u003eAseel ek timeless fragrance hai, jo daily wear, namaz aur special occasions ke liye perfect choice hai.\u003c\/p\u003e\n\u003cp\u003eAlcohol-free formula hone ki wajah se ye skin-friendly hai aur fragrance ka natural depth long time tak rehta hai.\u003c\/p\u003e\n\u003cp\u003eKey Features\u003c\/p\u003e\n\u003cp\u003eFragrance Type: Warm, Woody \u0026amp; Traditional\u003c\/p\u003e\n\u003cp\u003eQuantity: 6 ml Roll On\u003c\/p\u003e\n\u003cp\u003eAlcohol Free\u003c\/p\u003e\n\u003cp\u003eStrong \u0026amp; Long Lasting\u003c\/p\u003e\n\u003cp\u003ePremium roll-on glass bottle\u003c\/p\u003e\n\u003cp\u003eSuitable for men \u0026amp; women\u003c\/p\u003e\n\u003cp\u003eWhy Choose Aseel Attar\u003c\/p\u003e\n\u003cp\u003eClassic aur powerful fragrance\u003c\/p\u003e\n\u003cp\u003eLong-lasting performance\u003c\/p\u003e\n\u003cp\u003eHeadache-free traditional smell\u003c\/p\u003e\n\u003cp\u003ePremium packaging, gifting ke liye bhi suitable\u003c\/p\u003e\n\u003cp\u003eHow to Use\u003c\/p\u003e\n\u003cp\u003eNeck, wrist ya pulse points par halka sa roll karein aur rich fragrance enjoy karein.\u003c\/p\u003e","brand":"AL-SAALIM PERFUMES","offers":[{"title":"Default Title","offer_id":50472865399031,"sku":null,"price":179.0,"currency_code":"INR","in_stock":true}],"thumbnail_url":"\/\/cdn.shopify.com\/s\/files\/1\/0923\/0755\/4551\/files\/57B817DC-B18E-4CFD-9CB9-1CD98B192A51.png?v=1777870290","url":"https:\/\/alsaalimperfume.shop\/products\/aseel-attar-roll-on-6ml-al-saalim-perfumers-alcohol-free","provider":"AL-SAALIM PERFUMES","version":"1.0","type